			active_lock_reason: null,
			body: "### Description\n\nWhen Tooltip wraps a disabled Button, the tooltip is (sometimes?) hard to trigger. In attached example, it only seems to trigger when entering the button from the right. After it displays, it never goes away again. Triggering another tooltip would clear it though.\r\n\r\nOnly seems to be an issue in Safari.\r\n\r\nIf you pass shouldWrapChildren to the Tooltip component, then it behaves as expected.\n\n### Link to Reproduction\n\nhttps://play.chakra-ui.com/playground?code=N4Igxg9gJgpiBcICWBbADhATgFwATFwCEBXbbCAOwBpcAVCCAG2yTRoGEALAQwGtNuABUwQAbkliZcAX1wAzESlwByAAJge-bgFpiSAPSYY3MNmUAdCpZgAPDDlyQKAZzwBBNGlwBeXAAoASh8APnxLXFx9fVxyJhYvJGdcHkwoGIgYzCQAc2yYKSQKXABlbjluLP8YCmx8+UVcLOzObACqcMjogCNSXAB3TmrcJDwoCBhnGhHcChhROuzxpO4+7gBPXG5s7kKOo2xiTCK-DoiAHi4+AWExCXzg04jcM-o41lxGbi6YRm9zEAAcnM6pw7klCiUyhUkP8HkUngiziQyJRhs4ACKJL6MGBQYLI8gUM76AmUOEI876V7MVjkp7Ey5aG7iSR0gKWaSWEDSIA\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Go to attached link\r\n2. Hover mouse over button from bottom, observe nothing happens\r\n3. Hover instead from the side (the right)\r\n4. Tooltip appears\r\n5. Remove mouse from button\r\n6. Tooltip persists\r\n\n\n### Chakra UI Version\n\n2.7.0\n\n### Browser\n\nSafari 16.4\n\n### Operating System\n\n- [X] macOS\n- [ ] Windows\n- [ ] Linux\n\n### Additional Information\n\n_No response_",
